*specimen-0.5.2_rc3 (28 Jul 2007)

  28 Jul 2007; Samuli Suominen <drac@gentoo.org> +specimen-0.5.2_rc3.ebuild:
  Version bump; Use optimizations from make.conf instead of upstream -O3,
  strip -Werror, install desktop entry, change homepage, and more.

  11 Feb 2007; Diego Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> specimen-0.4.5.ebuild:
  Don't depend on virtual/alsa (those are drivers), depend properly on
  media-libs/alsa-lib.

